izedScore":50,"unit":"percent of applicable source layers with usable evidence","sourceIds":["statcan-business-counts-33101095","statcan-rd-performers-27100049","dnd-dcb-2025","canadabuys-tenders","canadabuys-awards","open-contracts"],"methodology":"3 of 6 applicable source layers are measured or provide Canada-wide public context for this capability-region pair.","caveat":"Coverage measures what the Atlas can currently support with source-backed data. It does not prove that missing activity is absent."}}'::jsonb,
